productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Albertina has one of these. She works as a gardener and she says it looks humongous.
i use it biweekly when i'm in my greenhouse.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 kilometer and weights 11 pound!
I saw one of these in Cote d'Ivoire and I bought one.
This Human works certainly well. It excitedly improves my football by a lot.
